<div style="margin: 0 0 30px; text-align:left;">
  <h1 style="margin: 0; background-color: #492e87; color: #fff; font-weight: normal; padding: 20px 35px;">You're invited to join Crowdstaffing</h1>
</div>
<div style="text-align: left; padding: 0 35px;">
  <p>
  Hi <%= @resource.first_name %>,
  </p>
  <p>
  <% if @resource.internal_user? %>
    <p>
      We are pleased to inform you that <%= @resource.created_by ? @resource.created_by.first_name : "System" %> have invited you to join crowdstaffing
    </p>
    <p>
      We congratulate, welcome you and wish you luck on behalf of our company and management.
    </p>
  <% elsif @resource.agency_user? %>
    <p>
      You've been invited to join Crowdstaffing as a member of <b><%= @resource.agency.company_name %></b>.
    </p>
  <% else %>
    <p>
      We are excited to invite you to Crowdstaffing! To complete your profile and gain access to the system, please simply click the “Accept Invitation” button below. If you have any questions or need assistance of any kind, please feel free to contact us at <a href="mailto:support@crowdstaffing.com">support@crowdstaffing.com</a>.
    </p>
  <% end %>
  <br />
  <div style="margin: 20px 0; text-align: center;">
    <a href='<%="#{@user.front_end_host}#/signup?token=#{@token}" %>' target="_blank" style="display: inline-block; color: #fff; background-color: #492e87; border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none;">Accept Invitation
    </a>
  </div>
  <br />
  If you are unable to direct to the page please copy paste the following link into your browser address bar.
  <br />
  <%="#{@user.front_end_host}#/signup?token=#{@token}" %>
  <br />
  </p>
  <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #e1e2e3; margin: 30px 0 20px;">
  <p>Thanks,</p>
