        <div>Crowdstaffing</div>
        <div>P:&nbsp;+1-844-467-2300 | E:&nbsp;<a href="mailto:support@crowdstaffing.com" target="_blank" style='color: black !important;text-decoration: none;'>support@crowdstaffing.com</a> | W:&nbsp;<a href="https://www.crowdstaffing.com" target="_blank" style='color: black !important;text-decoration: none;'>Crowdstaffing.com</a></div>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</div>
